      "date": "2013-03-13 07:06:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.9/x86_64, CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e42869d4-8ba9-11e2-aa89-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
